title: Expert raises eyebrows with prediction for Tesla's future: 'Weird transition period'
content:
The credit, which expires on Sept. 30, drove Tesla sales so high that Sherwood reported that the automaker was running out of inventory in late August.
Increased sales, along with a $1 billion stock purchase from Musk, could mark a turning point for the EV maker.
"We're in this weird transition period where we will lose a lot of incentives in the US," Musk said to investors, per Sherwood.
Despite the loss of the EV incentive, Teslas and other EVs are a great choice for both potential financial savings and environmental benefits.
Unfortunately, EVs face an uncertain fourth quarter of sales after the incentive ends on Sept. 30.

title: Karwa Chauth 2025 Date: Check shubh muhurat, rituals and significance for married women
content:
SynopsisKarwa Chauth Date 2025: Karwa Chauth 2025 will be observed on October 10th, with married women fasting without water for their husbands' long lives and marital happiness.
The auspicious puja time is from 5:16 PM to 6:29 PM, and the fast concludes after moonrise at 7:42 PM.
The day begins with Sargi, a pre-dawn meal from the mother-in-law.
